Class CallZone

  • java.lang.Object
    • eecs2030.pe2.CallZone

  • public class CallZone
extends java.lang.Object
    A class that specifies a set of call zones for making long distance calls using phone cards. The valid call zones are identified by the given static constants.
    Author:
    EECS2030
